{"tid":2175524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍創意戰艦展現大國創意， 支那又贏x2","createTime":"2020-08-26T13:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T14:08:41.000Z","uid":36861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"86abb72a12a1c5130a23376fa271e6c2fa177b06","tid":2175524,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:49:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3269287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3269287&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=14ebd65d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3269287&h=7431e813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3269287</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ijktEa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ijktEa.jpg&h=49ba3df6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qNvzx5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqNvzx5Q.jpg&h=aafbe63a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0vHRAjb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0vHRAjb.jpg&h=d83f36bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看圖說故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a6baa53c493dc5cf6dd8a3da09eaa434f11d4a","tid":2175524,"uid":9193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:49:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61ffee452a4fc0c1d4c0a0c1e60f6622f9b8ce89","tid":2175524,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:50:22.000Z","msg":"應該係世上最有創意嘅戰艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78a0533670340f6c575c101b8665d9e3cb5282a","tid":2175524,"uid":297436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"Atlantic Conveyor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d476559e919146a2a1048d31e40052e40a45468","tid":2175524,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國官方近期頻發航行警告，在南海、東海、渤海展開軍演，美國知名軍事記者大衛．艾克斯（David Axe）在《富比士》刊文指出，近期注意到解放軍竟將商船改造成軍事用船，他認為：「中國艦隊展現了創意&mdash;&mdash;或是絕望。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國《央視軍事》本月19日釋出第71集團軍某陸航旅在黃海海域組織多機型訓練，包含海上補給線演訓，在船上指揮員引導下，中國直-8、武直-19飛行員依據海識訊息和船體方位，迅速調整飛行姿態，成功登上船艦，艦上人員立刻對直升機進行油料、彈藥補充，隨後直升機聽令起飛，再度投入戰場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《央視軍事》釋出的影片中，解放軍使用的是民用半潛式重載船「振華28號」，台灣海軍中校湯中龍在今年6月於《作戰研究》中指出，中共海軍首艘半潜船「東海島號（舷號868），是在2015年7月加入中共海軍，半潛船雖不像軍艦能裝置武器、具有攻擊能力，但因具有獨特的性能與廣泛的用途，因此成為世界各國爭相研發、建造的新式船舶。<br />\n<br />\n大衛．艾克斯說，北京幾十年來一直租用或借用商船，作為擴大其兩棲艦隊的便捷方法，開戰時可以迅速徵用數百艘有用的船隻，在直升機演習中，「振華28號」似乎是臨時飛行甲板，但不曉得解放軍花了多少時間才將船的甲板配置完成，中方正忙著打造75型突擊艦，可能會有台海、南海軍事用途，而目前看起來像「振華28號」這樣的船隻可能也會派上用場。"},{"pid":"55d59fcea08fc2e25bbe411b2f816b531e298f90","tid":2175524,"uid":278168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"61ffee452a4fc0c1d4c0a0c1e60f6622f9b8ce89","tid":2175524,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:50:22.000Z","msg":"應該係世上最有創意嘅戰艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:55:13.000Z","msg":"好似就嚟沉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cc8565822a558d23fbacf1941ce33f73c93013","tid":2175524,"uid":36861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZ0S4eS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZ0S4eS.jpg&h=c918fd88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75002eafc3c7c0bb2de023e5b614ace62a053e41","tid":2175524,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86abb72a12a1c5130a23376fa271e6c2fa177b06","tid":2175524,"uid":36861,"lik